snippet.title: Venus square Neptune - astro headlines - Harry & Meghan - Johnny Depp & Amber Heard - 27 July 2020
snippet.description:
Julian Venables the London Astrologer talks Daily Astrology for Astrology Enthusiasts.

In this video Julian talks about transit Venus in Gemini square transit Neptune in Pisces. 

Venus square Neptune appears in the newspaper headlines as Julian points out the planetary themes in today's news on 27 July 2020.

Julia then goes on to reflect on the headlines and how events in your own life might be reflected by the relationship confusion, or values confusion that Venus square Neptune can contain.
